title: The Stonehenges (7" Stretch)
body_html:
If that prehistoric monument was a pair of shorts. Sorta.

Whether you're going for an aggressive power walk, hitting the slip n slide, or on the way to a weekend brunch, these every day shorts are just that, good for every day. These shorts have a 7" inseam.

Let's talk deets:

  • 4-way stretch for extreme mobility
  • 85% polyester, 15% spandex
  • Zip close back pocket, to keep all your goods safe
  • Meshpocketing for quick drying
  • Linerless for extra comfort
  • Equipped with a drawcord to keep 'em tight for any activity

title: Gift Card

title: The Texas
body_html: We built a Texas time travel machine and went back to spring break '77 on South Padre Island. This is the only thing we managed to bring back. Tbh...we were lucky to get back to the time machine.

title: The Lone Star Swim Trunks
body_html: Trunks engineered to make you feel like you're singing to a sold out crowd at Gruene Hall after spending the day floating down the Guadalupe River. Texas Forever.

title: The Office Party
body_html:
Be your own Christmas tree in these Griswold-approved holiday chubberalls.

Mens Light Up Overall Shorts

Fit:
We recommend ordering the same size as the casual shorts you wear in the size guide.

Details:
-Made from 100% printed Pine Tree denim
-Adjustable straps to fit almost everyone, no matter how tall you are!
-2 side pockets, one chest pocket & a zipper fly for quick bathroom breaks.

-Overalls come with the light strand and instructions on how to string this bad boy. Battery pack takes 3 AA batteries (not included).


-We have to tell you that you CANNOT wash the lights or the battery pack, because electronics don't like water (or any liquid really, including egg nog).
